{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 16}\uc1\u8220*But blessed are your eyes, for they see, and your ears, for they hear;{\super\f1\cf2\fs24 17}for I tell you that many prophets and good people have longed for the sight of the things which you are seeing, yet never saw them, and to hear the things which you are hearing, yet never heard them.
